{"tid":1231973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明天早點回來！","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T14:44:47.000Z","uid":140121,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39abc969862416f547cb7b943e4d5bd025487b43","tid":1231973,"uid":140121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"知道一定有好多人走左，如果有心，你宜家就去訓，聽日一早就返黎接力，等你。"},{"pid":"198660b842b6d982edbd9bd4240764b2919a9004","tid":1231973,"uid":157938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=bb6bb1de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4650116c92552be789a38a13c50f2013136dbe87","tid":1231973,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d76444bce6f733268586aa6a392332f1c9b213af","tid":1231973,"uid":140121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:13:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"609a3bdd497e2f0373995f50f97bc605b0d96a85","tid":1231973,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"收到！"},{"pid":"40aa789f9b62963f31b7af1c8951679c2052e1d5","tid":1231973,"uid":140121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af5c63da9d07e58efd9ee5153e51d0ef33a03338","tid":1231973,"uid":140121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf9ac7f0b70a461814127932ee87c0d9dd13c507","tid":1231973,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見"},{"pid":"1d41c48dab4142b002b4fd17749b3855b22c2ffd","tid":1231973,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c3e306c7c986d8842a1a1c58d2ecae36748418c6","tid":1231973,"uid":140121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}